  "text": "The vehicle body is modeled as a single rigidbody component with mass-inertia properties as given in [CITATION_1] . As stated earlier, both the vehicle mass-inertia properties and the masses of the individual subsystems are known. Simplified geometry like that in Figure 4 was used to calculate each subsystem's respective moment of inertia values.",
